what:
where:
Abu Dhabi
Our client has been established in the Middle East for over 30 years and prides itself on offering client's a transparent, professional and high quality service across all areas. This established full service brand is well renowned across the GCC region and has attracted a number of high profile real estate professionals over the last few years.
Due to growth, our client is looking to strengthen its Abu Dhabi offering by recruiting a property manager to join its established team. You will be tasked with:
Ensuring budget guidelines are followed consistently Daily communication and collaboration with staff, regional managers and others as needed Overseeing and directing all administrative duties in accordance with company policy Site inspections Liaising with Landlords and Tenants Dealing with inventories and check - in procedures
Experience working in the Middle East, ideally the UAE and the ability to speak and write in Arabic is essential. Any property managers applying for this post must be able to drive and have a car.
Our client is offering between AED 18,000 and 20,000 per month along with progression opportunities.
Please apply online or for further information, contact Azara Roger at Cobalt Recruitment on +971 26113019.
